videos.headline: K. Johnson run for 3 yds for a TD
videos.description: Kerryon Johnson run for 3 yds for a TD

videos.headline: Auburn LB Deshaun Davis is ejected for targeting
videos.description: Shurmur, Kyle pass incomplete to Lipscomb, Kalija, PENALTY AUBURN personal foul (Davis, Deshaun) 15 yards to the VANDERBILT37, NO PLAY, 1ST DOWN VANDERBILT.

videos.headline: Deshaun Davis ejected for targeting
videos.description: Auburn LB Deshaun Davis is ejected for targeting after his hit on Vanderbilt WR Kalija Lipscomb. Davis would walk off the field pumping up the crowd.

videos.headline: Vanderbilt QB Kyle Shurmur tosses 8-yard TD pass
videos.description: Vanderbilt QB Kyle Shurmur throws an 8-yard touchdown pass to TE Jared Pinkey early in the second quarter.

videos.headline: White finds Slayton open to give Auburn the lead
videos.description: Sean White throws a frozen rope to a wide open Darius Slayton in the end zone to put Auburn ahead 17-13.

videos.headline: Auburn 53 yard field goal extends their lead to 7
Auburn RB Kamryn Pettway injured on 60 yard run
videos.description: Kamryn Pettway run for 60 yds to the Vandy 12 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Cunningham hurdles everyone for awesome blocked FG
videos.description: Zach Cunningham times his leap perfectly, jumping over the entire line and blocking the field goal attempt for Vanderbilt in spectacular fashion.

videos.headline: Auburn's INT seals game for the Tigers
videos.description: Auburn DB Joshua Holsey picks off Vanderbilt QB Kyle Shurmur's pass to cap the victory for the Tigers.

videos.headline: Auburn fends off Vanderbilt
videos.description: An injured Sean White came off the bench to throw a touchdown pass and Josh Holsey intercepted a last-minute throw to lift No. 9 Auburn to a come-from-behind win over Vanderbilt.
